<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Whereverthe Weather</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <script src='https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js'></script>
 <style>
  /* Make the image fully responsive */
  .carousel-inner img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 80px;
  }
  </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container-fluid m-4">
   
      <div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-3"></div>
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="card shadow">
  <div class="card-header text-center bg-info text-light "><h3>
    Wherever the Weather
    </h3></div>
  <div class="card-body text-center"><fieldset>
    
<div class="container mt-3">

<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">

 
  
  <!-- The slideshow -->
  <div class="carousel-inner m-2 text-center">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
<i class='fas fa-bolt text-warning' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-cloud-meatball text-danger' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-cloud-moon text-info' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
     <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-cloud-moon-rain text-dark' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
     <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-cloud-rain text-primary' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-cloud-showers-heavy text-secondary' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-cloud-sun text-warning' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-cloud-sun-rain text-muted' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-rainbow text-dark' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-smog	 text-secondary' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-snowflake text-primary' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='far fa-snowflake text-info' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
     <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-sun text-warning' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
     <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='far fa-sun text-danger' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-water text-primary' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
     <div class="carousel-item">
<i class='fas fa-wind	 text-secondary' style='font-size:65px'></i>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  
</div>

</div>
   <p>
     
    <form action="/" method="post">
          <input name="city" type="text" class="ghost-input" placeholder="Enter a City" required>
      <input type="submit" class="ghost-button bg-info text-light" value="Get Weather"></p>
      
      <% if(weather !== null){ %>
          <p class="m-1 text-secondary"><%= weather %></p>
        <% } %>
        

        <% if(error !== null){ %>
          <p><%= error %></p>
        <% } %>
      </fieldset>
        </form></div>
  <div class="card-footer bg-light text-secondary">
    
<p class="m-2"><small>
Hey, I'm San and this is my first NodeJS web app. I used a stack of Node, Express and EJS. My framework is Bootstrap 4. <a href="https://codeburst.io/build-a-weather-website-in-30-minutes-with-node-js-express-openweather-a317f904897b">Link to the tutorial I followed.</a>I love cards. I love making weather apps, so expect more. I have a lot of spare time.</small> </p>
</div>
    
   </div>
  <div class="col-sm-3"></div>
</div>
      
     </div>
   
    
<script>
$(document).ready(function(){
  // Activate Carousel
  $("#myCarousel").carousel();
  
});
</script>
    
    <footer class="m-4">
    <a href="http://glitch.com">Made with Glitch!</a>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
